# UI test writing (X01 & Cricket)

Full phased backlog: [`docs/testing/x01-cricket-ui-test-phased-plan.md`](../../docs/testing/x01-cricket-ui-test-phased-plan.md)

## Test pyramid

| Layer | Owns |
|-------|------|
| **Unit** | Scoring math, turn order, bust/checkout, match completion, `GameplayLayout` predicates |
| **UI** | Pad → board feedback, navigation, layout contracts, a11y identifier presence |
| **WCAG** | Touch targets, labels, audit filters (`WCAGAccessibilityUITests`) |

Do **not** duplicate game rules in UI tests. Assert **observable UI state** (combined accessibility labels, pad enabled/disabled).

## Base class & launch

- Subclass `DartBuddyUITestCase` (not raw `XCTestCase`) unless writing WCAG audits.
- Default args: `-ui_test_reset`, `-disable_firebase_analytics`.
- Roster: `-seed_players` (Alice, Bob, Carol).
- Bots: add `-ui_test_instant_bots` + `-ui_test_disable_feedback` (see `UITestRegressionHelpers`).
- X01 speed: `configureFastX01MatchForUITest` (101 / double-out / 1 leg).

## Query order (stable → brittle)

1. `accessibilityIdentifier` — `pad_20`, `cricket_enter`, `scoreCard_active`, `startMatchButton`
2. Combined element `.label` fragments — `assertActiveScoreCardLabel`, `assertActiveCricketColumnLabel`
3. Visible text / alerts — last resort; prefer adding an identifier in the view

## Waits (required after turns)

```swift
_ = waitForPadReady(app, timeout: timeout + 15)           // X01
waitForCricketScoringPadReady(app, timeout: timeout + 5)  // Cricket
waitForX01MatchBoard(in: app, timeout: ...)               // board landmark
```

Use `element.wait(for: \.isEnabled, toEqual: true, ...)` for bot-turn recovery.

## Where logic lives

| Concern | File |
|---------|------|
| Tab, setup, pad landmarks | `UITestMenuSupport.swift` |
| Fast X01 presets, WCAG flows | `WCAGAccessibilitySupport.swift` |
| Bot regression, landscape helpers | `UITestRegressionHelpers.swift` |
| 3-player starters, cricket chips | `UITestMatchSetupHelpers.swift` |

**Thin test files:** one behavior per `test*` method; shared sequences go in helpers.

## Naming

- Class: `{Feature}UITests`
- Method: `test{Behavior}{Condition}` — e.g. `testX01TripleScoringUpdatesRemaining`
- Reference regressions: commit hash or regression catalog row in `docs/testing/x01-cricket-ui-test-phased-plan.md`

## Avoid

- Frame assertions except **layout regression** (landscape pad below pinned board); run those on **iPhone 17 Pro Max** only.
- Full multi-player match completion in UI when unit tests already cover it.
- Duplicating WCAG pad-contract tests in feature suites.
- `continueAfterFailure = true`.

## CI tiers

| Tier | Suite | Simulator |
|------|-------|-----------|
| PR (`DartBuddyCI`) | `Lean1_0SmokeUITests` + WCAG | iPhone 17 |
| Nightly | `X01MatchUITests`, `CricketMatchUITests`, `RegressionUITests` landscape | iPhone 17 Pro Max for landscape |
